{"tid":248044,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係雞係公廁","createTime":"2017-05-18T09:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T13:58:31.000Z","uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"158a79db101709a21f17a8e97311755e0cc53462","tid":248044,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"雖然有時聽到女人係雞係公廁覺得好un耳<br />\n但身邊啲人係咁派帽<br />\n都未有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知我咁諗好衰<br />\n但咁樣對啲對感情認真既人公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲女人係撚咁派帽 但又唔係靚 格又臭 啲仔都死心塌地 桃花一籮籮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d467c87de63fba3b834668905c51a7e3be15ff8","tid":248044,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217cf9531c1d9f976c90f59f1018a43001f2238c","tid":248044,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"你都係想講你無仔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7798ba683bff008e10fc93aa069df216f245059d","tid":248044,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"2541ac357c696b12ffdf743e0e0801ce6bd7ba3a","tid":248044,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"唔係靚=至少正常樣<br />\n格又臭=對住男人唔係咁<br />\n完"},{"pid":"1702f30a268a37311d3645333ba3d50c70d8a418","tid":248044,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都係想講你無仔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但成日都會驚佢俾人勾走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18ca29582aa7616f4173a249eee2a480cc2a633","tid":248044,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"13a80d6a0616fe1ac7753bdce9a3d358a13035cc","tid":248044,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span></blockquote><br />\n有時都想知男人識唔識分臭雞 識啲人 有仔都照同出面啲人扑野 但啲男人都係搶住幫佢埋單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b7b4dda048ff1de695ee5668d2126bf9527a8e","tid":248044,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"00ade6fde4ef0fe0551d031fd4e6089d4b926701","tid":248044,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係靚=至少正常樣<br />\n格又臭=對住男人唔係咁<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n我識條女話條仔帶佢去食麥記譚仔果啲會閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗對住男人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}